{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7025efab86","title":"对李维汉在民族宗教问题上主要言论摘录的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"dbbeec4c14","index":0,"year":1964,"month":9,"day":11,"articleId":"7025efab86"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji47","name":"毛泽东全集第47卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/47-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji47":{"comments":[{"id":"f477ef6b5c","publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"7025efab86","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"中共中央统战部办公室1964年9月3日印发的中央统战部部长李维汉（即罗迈）关于民族宗教问题的主要言论摘录共分八个问题：一、改革和平频问题：二、宗教问题；三、区域自治问题；四、班禅问题：五、上层统一战线问题；六、新疆问题；七、民族关系、民族主义等问题；八、社会主义民族问题。这个言论摘录当时是用来批判李维汉的。1964年9月3日，中央统战部副部长徐冰为报送这个材料，给中共中央政治局委员、中央书记处书记彭真写了一封信。信中说：“送上罗迈同志关于民族宗教问题的言论，文学不多，还容易看。请审阅，如认为可以，则请送主席阅。书记处和政治局常委我们另外送。彭真将徐冰的信和李维汉言论摘录送毛泽东后，毛泽东在这封信上写了批语。"}],"contents":[{"id":"0e6ed07a55","type":"title","text":"对李维汉在民族宗教问题上主要言论摘录\"的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"7025efab86"},{"id":"f477ef6b5c","type":"paragraph","text":"徐冰同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"7025efab86"},{"id":"5a5dab3aa3","type":"paragraph","text":"希你坚持阶级立场，团结大多数同志，叫他们千方不要动摇","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"7025efab86"},{"id":"fadc5b7c81","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"7025efab86"},{"id":"afd3ef2723","type":"paragraph","text":"九月十一日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"7025efab86"},{"id":"57f23256ca","type":"paragraph","text":"退徐冰同志。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"7025efab86"}],"page":{"id":"8e589fb376","publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"7025efab86","start":147,"end":147}}}},"__N_SSG":true}